DEFINITIONS

"Software" means the DroneAware feeder node software, including all source
code, compiled binaries, scripts, configuration files, and documentation
distributed in this repository.

"Feeder Node" means a hardware device running this Software for the sole
purpose of capturing and transmitting drone Remote ID telemetry data to the
DroneAware network.

"Competing Service" means any product, platform, or service that aggregates,
resells, or redistributes drone Remote ID telemetry data as a primary business
function, other than the DroneAware network operated by DroneAware, LLC.

